--- !u!114 &1509291756
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1509291755}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2330b6f59de4c2349ad2089aeb64866f, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::UIPromptController
  pages:
  - pageName: Page 1
    pageText: From the given materials, select the materials which you would require
      to conduct this experiment.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 1
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 1142061880}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 2
    pageText: Select the glassware and the solutions which you would require for
      this experiment.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 1
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 1936092262}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 3
    pageText: Select the plant which has long and thin leaves to carry out the experiment.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 1
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 0}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 4
    pageText: Now let's keep the plant in the dark for around 48 hrs to destarch
      it.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 1
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 0}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 5
    pageText: Now let's keep the plant in the dark for around 48 hrs to destarch
      it.
    showDialogBox: 0
    showAlternatePanels: 1
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 476846386}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 6
    pageText: Why do we use a destarched plant to conduct this experiment? Click
      on the highlighted leaf to find out.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 1
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 396460629}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
    - panel: {fileID: 0}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
    - panel: {fileID: 300781152}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 7
    pageText: For carrying out photosynthesis experiments, we need to be sure that
      all traces of starch are removed
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 1
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 396460629}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 8
    pageText: Tap on any one of the molecules
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 1
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 396460629}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 9
    pageText: Drag the potassium hydroxide (KOH) solution towards the boiling tube
      to fill 1/5th of it.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 1
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 0}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 1
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 10
    pageText: Drag the boiling tube filled with the KOH solution towards the clamp
      of laboratory stand.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 0
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 396460629}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 11
    pageText: Drag the laboratory stand towards the highlighted leaf.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 0
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 396460629}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 12
    pageText: Drag the split cork to the mouth of the boiling tube to fix the leaf.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 0
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 396460629}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 13
    pageText: Drag the spatula towards the petroleum jelly.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 0
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 396460629}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 14
    pageText: Drag the spatula containing petroleum jelly towards the mouth of the
      boiling tube.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 0
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 396460629}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 15
    pageText: Drag the spatula containing petroleum jelly towards the mouth of the
      boiling tube.
    showDialogBox: 0
    showAlternatePanels: 1
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 1485972523}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 16
    pageText: Tap on the tube with KOH to know what is happening inside.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 0
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 1485972523}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
  - pageName: Page 17
    pageText: Drag the molecule of carbon dioxide to the KOH molecule to complete
      the reaction.
    showDialogBox: 1
    showAlternatePanels: 0
    alternatePanels:
    - panel: {fileID: 1485972523}
      stayInUpcomingPages: 0
      enableOnce: 0
      hasBeenEnabledOnce: 0
